#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli inkluderer indbyggede instruktioner i appen for at hjælpe dig med at "
"konfigurere og administrere din opsætning."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Denne side giver et overblik over nøglefunktioner og direkte links til, hvor"
" de kan administreres."

